{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/frontend/1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a1297795-028f-5255-a541-800dfa01fb87","html":"<h2 id=\"상태-관리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C-%EA%B4%80%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"상태 관리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>상태 관리</h2>\n<p>프론트엔드에서 엔터프라이즈급 어플리케이션을 만들기위해 상태관리 툴은 거의 필수적인 느낌입니다. 무지성으로 사용하던 Redux나 Vuex같은 상태관리 툴의 동작방식을 알아보는 좋은 기회가 될것 같습니다.</p>\n<p>상태관리 툴을 사용하는 대표적인 이유로 <strong>상태관리가 복잡해지고 컴포넌트의 Depth가 깊어</strong>져 props로 단방향 처리나 이벤트 함수를 통해 올려보내는 식의 상태조작은 한계가 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이 때 <code class=\"language-text\">중앙 집중식 저장소 역할을 하면 예측 가능한 방식으로 상태를 변경</code> 할 수 있도록 도와주는 상태관리 툴들의 기본적인 동작 방식을 알아봅니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"observer-pattern-발행구독-패턴pubsub\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#observer-pattern-%EB%B0%9C%ED%96%89%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%85-%ED%8C%A8%ED%84%B4pubsub\" aria-label=\"observer pattern 발행구독 패턴pubsub permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Observer Pattern? 발행/구독 패턴(Pub/Sub)?</h3>\n<p>이 둘의 패턴이 같다라고 하는 글도 보였고 반대다?라는 글도 보여서 혼란스럽습니다. 뭔가 각잡고 파지 않으면 이상하게 기억될 것 같아 무서운데.. 일단 간단하게 이해한 느낌은</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 527px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/44385/observer_pub_sub.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.41666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/8ac56/observer_pub_sub.webp 240w,\n/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/d3be9/observer_pub_sub.webp 480w,\n/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/042cc/observer_pub_sub.webp 527w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 527px) 100vw, 527px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/8ff5a/observer_pub_sub.png 240w,\n/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/e85cb/observer_pub_sub.png 480w,\n/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/44385/observer_pub_sub.png 527w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 527px) 100vw, 527px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a37a089715720805ab6c8e885af561a8/44385/observer_pub_sub.png\"\n          alt=\"observer pub sub\"\n          title=\"observer pub sub\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"observer-pattern\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#observer-pattern\" aria-label=\"observer pattern permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Observer Pattern</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>결합도가 높은데 이유가 Subject에 Observer들이 등록되어 직접 알려줌으로 서로를 인지하고 있어야 하기 때문인것 같습니다.</li>\n<li>상태의 궁굼증과 상관없이 항상 통보받습니다.</li>\n<li>동기적으로 작동합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"pubsub-pattern발행구독-모델\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pubsub-pattern%EB%B0%9C%ED%96%89%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%85-%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8\" aria-label=\"pubsub pattern발행구독 모델 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pub/Sub Pattern(발행/구독 모델)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Pub/Sub 패턴은 관찰자와 관찰대상 이 외에 추가적인 컴포넌트가 존재하는데 여기서 관찰자와 관찰대상의 소통을 담당한다.</li>\n<li>위와 같은 이유로 Observer Pattern보다 결합도가 낮다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"objectdefinepropertyobject-prop-descriptor\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#objectdefinepropertyobject-prop-descriptor\" aria-label=\"objectdefinepropertyobject prop descriptor permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Object.defineProperty(object, prop, descriptor)</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>객체에 직접 새로운 속성을 정의하거나 이미 존재하는 속성을 수정한 후, 그 객체를 반환합니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>위와 같은 정의를 가지고 있지만 우리가 여기에서 사용할 기능은 매개변수 <code class=\"language-text\">descriptor</code>에서 get, set을 이용해 값의 변화에 따라 관찰자를 통한 함수 실행입니다.</p>\n<p>여러가지 속성이 있는데 이 부분은 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/defineProperty#%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">MDN</a>에서 확인해 봅시다!</p>\n<p>(추가적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">defineProperty</code>는 IE를 지원하기위한 문법입니다. 최신 브라우저에서는 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Proxy</a>를 이용하면 더 쉽게 만들 수 있습니다. )</p>\n<h4 id=\"예제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"예제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예제</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> state <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  a<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  b<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> stateKeys <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">keys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">observer</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">a + b = </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> state<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>b<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> key <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> stateKeys<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> _value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> state<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">defineProperty</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> _value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      _value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">observer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">observer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nstate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nstate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 코드를 통해 우리가 관찰하고 싶은 상태가 값이 변할 때마다 observer가 실행됨을 볼 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이런 구조의 코드를 함수화 하여 중앙 저장소의 값을 관찰하면, 구독되어있는 컴포넌트들에 전역으로 쉽게 상태를 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"flux-패턴\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flux-%ED%8C%A8%ED%84%B4\" aria-label=\"flux 패턴 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Flux 패턴</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 820px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/9f82e/flux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/8ac56/flux.webp 240w,\n/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/d3be9/flux.webp 480w,\n/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/b1f58/flux.webp 820w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/8ff5a/flux.png 240w,\n/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/e85cb/flux.png 480w,\n/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/9f82e/flux.png 820w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8ef687083384d183ff57c029daa5a6c4/9f82e/flux.png\"\n          alt=\"flux\"\n          title=\"flux\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Vuex와 Redux에서 사용되는 패턴입니다. 특징은 기존 다른 패턴들과 다르게 <strong>단방향흐름</strong>을 가지고있습니다.</p>\n<p>이전의 패턴들에서 문제는 대표적으로 Facebook 알림(notification) 버그가 있었다고 합니다. 양방향에 비동기적으로 변경이 생길 수 있었고 예측이 힘들어 디버깅이 어려웠던 근본적인 문제를 Flux를 통해 해결했다고 합니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bestalign.github.io/translation/cartoon-guide-to-flux/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">여기</a>에서 flux패턴설명을 재밌게 봤습니다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"참고자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고자료 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고자료</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://junilhwang.github.io/TIL/Javascript/Design/Vanilla-JS-Store/#_1-%E1%84%8C%E1%85%AE%E1%86%BC%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A1%E1%86%BC-%E1%84%8C%E1%85%B5%E1%86%B8%E1%84%8C%E1%85%AE%E1%86%BC%E1%84%89%E1%85%B5%E1%86%A8-%E1%84%89%E1%85%A1%E1%86%BC%E1%84%90%E1%85%A2%E1%84%80%E1%85%AA%E1%86%AB%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">바닐라로 상태관리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://bestalign.github.io/translation/cartoon-guide-to-flux/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">flux 패턴</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/frontend/1","tagSlugs":["/tag/javascript/","/tag/frontend/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-10-09T00:00:00","description":"상태관리를 이해하기 위한 여러가지 개념들","tags":["javascript","Frontend"],"title":"상태관리 1","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/624cc4a835e68430a8beec01cef8ac6c/photo.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/frontend/1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}